Posts.Content: I had Stage 2 breast cancer 14 years ago at age 55.  Had a lumpectomy, radiation and 5 years of tamoxifen.  Was diagnosed with Stage 4 metastatic breast cancer in May, 2012 with mets to the liver.  I am triple positive.  Might be absolutely nothing, but I would get in for a biopsy asap.
Posts.Title: Breast cancer recurrence after 10-years
